name: Planet DOGE
description: Planet DOGE is unlike any other in the vast and ever-growing crypto galaxy, as its colonies were created through humour and parody. The astronauts were unbothered by the planet's properties as they were in admiration and worship for the foundational humor, cuteness, and memes produced by the planet's citizens. Its powerful and indestructible community further developed the planet into a unique powerhouse of the crypto galaxy.
